Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.72,0:04:22.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,大衛，睜開你的...\N{\rENG}David, open your...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.16,0:04:27.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,那麼, 我猜 空蕩的街道意味著孤獨吧\N{\rENG}Well, I suppose the empty street meant loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:30.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,你是個精神病專家,應該有更好的分析\N{\rENG}You're a shrink. You gotta do better than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:34.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,我是個醫生, 我倆別互相存有偏見\N{\rENG}I'm a doctor.Let's not stereotype each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:37.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,不是所有的有錢少爺都空虛...\N{\rENG}Not all rich kids are soulless and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.40,0:04:40.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,也不是所有的心理醫生都會解夢\N{\rENG}not all psychologists care about dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.57,0:04:45.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,問題是你怎麼會在這裡, 為什麼會被指控\N{\rENG}The question is how you got here and why you've been charged.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.21,0:04:48.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,你想知道什麼? 我快滿33歲了\N{\rENG}What do you want to know? I was about to turn 33.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:52.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,擁有三家雜誌社和一家全球性的出版社\N{\rENG}I ran three magazines and a worldwide publishing house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.12,0:04:57.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,大部分日子裡我都愚昧的認為這一切都是永恆的\N{\rENG}Most days I fooled myself into believing it would last forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:04:59.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,年輕不都是這樣嗎?\N{\rENG}Isn't that what being young is about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.03,0:05:02.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,自以為你就是...\N{\rENG}Believing secretly that you would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.33,0:05:05.19,CHT,,0,0,0,,歷史上唯一的那個...\N{\rENG}the one person in the history of man...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.30,0:05:07.13,CHT,,0,0,0,,長生不老的人\N{\rENG}who would live forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:13.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,你這麼早去哪兒?\N{\rENG}Where you going so early?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.11,0:05:15.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,別再往我的鬧鐘裡錄留言了, 好嗎?\N{\rENG}Don't record any more messages on my alarm clock, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:20.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 為什麼? - 我會以為我們結婚了\N{\rENG}- Why not? - I'll start to think we're married.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.58,0:05:22.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,別再提那個字眼, 我就不來這裡...\N{\rENG}Don't ever say that word. I will never come over...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.95,0:05:25.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,給你帶雞湯, 又讓你欲仙欲死\N{\rENG}and bring you chicken soup and fuck your brains out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.59,0:05:29.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,你感冒好了嗎?\N{\rENG}How's your cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.59,0:05:32.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,還沒, 你呢?\N{\rENG}Still there. How 'bout yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.99,0:05:35.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,你真的讓我忘了自己在生病\N{\rENG}You definitely took my mind off it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.83,0:05:37.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,真的嗎?\N{\rENG}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.16,0:05:40.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,Yes!\N{\rENG}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.21,0:05:49.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,我是茱莉\N{\rENG}"Juliana" here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.31,0:05:52.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,嗨, 蕾娜, 我錯過試鏡了, 我一定是瘋了!\N{\rENG}Hi, Rayna. I missed my audition. I lost my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.71,0:05:55.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,不, 聽著, 我得掛了\N{\rENG}No, listen, I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.65,0:05:57.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,我在大衛這兒\N{\rENG}I'm with David.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:03.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,你自便吧, 瑪麗亞會來清理, 你走前設定警鈴\N{\rENG}Help yourself to whatever. Maria will clean up. Set the alarm before you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.02,0:06:06.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,還有...\N{\rENG}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.96,0:06:10.39,CHT,,0,0,0,,你是最棒的\N{\rENG}you are the greatest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.96,0:06:12.59,CHT,,0,0,0,,拜拜，甜心\N{\rENG}Bye, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:15.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,拜拜，甜心, 我額...再打給你\N{\rENG}Bye, honey. I'll call you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.93,0:06:16.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,幾時?\N{\rENG}When?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.57,0:06:20.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,-幾時?-很快! \N{\rENG}- When?- Soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:07.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,你訂了球場沒有?\N{\rENG}Did you reserve the court?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:10.59,CHT,,0,0,0,,鎮定, 這種時候我應付不了這麼複雜的會談\N{\rENG}Easy. I can't handle heavy conversation at this ungodly hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.69,0:07:14.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,抱歉這麼早做這些, 但我十點要打完\N{\rENG}Sorry to do this early, but I gotta be done by 10:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.43,0:07:18.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,你八點四十五趕不到了, 是嗎?\N{\rENG}You're not gonna make the 8.:45, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:19.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,-你怎麼找到我的?\N{\rENG}-大衛埃姆斯...\N{\rENG}- How did you find me? - David Aames...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.93,0:07:22.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,你要決定新一期的封面顏色\N{\rENG}you have to check the colors for the new issue of Rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.87,0:07:26.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 有什麼顏色?\N{\rENG}- 黃, 紅或傳統的白色\N{\rENG}- What are the colors? - Yellow and red or traditional white.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:31.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 我得想想看\N{\rENG}- 大衛, 拜託\N{\rENG}- Gotta think about it. - David, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:33.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,別遲到十點的董事會\N{\rENG}Don't be late for the 10.:00 with the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:36.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,好的, 但別告訴別人我在哪, 上帝打來我也不管\N{\rENG}Don't tell anybody where I am. I don't care if God calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.15,0:07:39.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 我很忙, 非常忙\N{\rENG}- Yeah - I'm very, very busy. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.12,0:07:46.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 你就不能廢掉董事會嗎?\N{\rENG}- 那七個小矮人? 不行\N{\rENG}- Can't you get rid of that board?\N{\rENG}- The Seven Dwarfs? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.93,0:07:48.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,那些人快把你逼瘋了\N{\rENG}Those people drive you nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.09,0:07:51.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,這是我老爸的意願, 他雇傭了他們\N{\rENG}And that was the desire of my father who hired them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:07:57.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,你又上了茱莉吉雅妮, 是嗎?\N{\rENG}You fucked Julie Gianni again, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.00,0:08:01.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,打電話時我就知道某人在\N{\rENG}I know someone was there when I called.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:03.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,你還用那種語氣\N{\rENG}You had that tone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.18,0:08:07.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,"沒啦，我感冒, 晚上想待在家."\N{\rENG}"No, I got a cold. I'm hanging in tonight, you know."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:08.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,我真的感冒了\N{\rENG}I had a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:12.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 只有我一個人\N{\rENG}- 好吧.\N{\rENG}- I was alone. - Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.52,0:08:15.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 這輩子你愛怎樣就怎樣\N{\rENG}- 謝謝.\N{\rENG}- You do what you want with your life. - Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.19,0:08:18.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,但有一天你會知道真愛是什麼\N{\rENG}But one day you'll know what love truly is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:20.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,它夾雜著心酸和甜蜜\N{\rENG}It's the sour and the sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:23.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,我嘗過心酸, 它讓我領會到甜蜜的滋味\N{\rENG}I know sour, which allows me to appreciate the sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:27.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,茱莉吉雅妮只是朋友\N{\rENG}Julie Gianni is a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.50,0:08:30.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,有時候我們一起上床\N{\rENG}Sometimes we sleep together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.87,0:08:33.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,幹嘛? 幹嘛?\N{\rENG}What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.81,0:08:36.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 幹嘛?\N{\rENG}- 我的夢中情人...\N{\rENG}- What? - My dream girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.74,0:08:38.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,茱莉吉雅妮...\N{\rENG}Julie Gianni...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.04,0:08:42.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,竟然是你的...炮友\N{\rENG}is your fuck buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:45.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 你想聽什麼?\N{\rENG}- 開慢點, 老兄\N{\rENG}- What do you wanna listen to?\N{\rENG}- Slow down, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:48.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,有什麼聽的?\N{\rENG}巴塞隆納...盧珀...\N{\rENG}What do we got here? Barcelona, Looper.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:50.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,電臺司令?\N{\rENG}Radiohead?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.02,0:08:52.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,小心! 小心!\N{\rENG}Look out! Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.86,0:09:00.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,操！\N{\rENG}Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.17,0:09:05.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們差點沒命\N{\rENG}We almost died.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.97,0:09:08.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 我知道\N{\rENG}- 你們他媽的看著點!\N{\rENG}- I know. - Use your fuckin' head!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.37,0:09:10.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,死亡就擺在我面前, 知道我看見什麼嗎?\N{\rENG}My own death was in front of me, and you know what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.84,0:09:13.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,你的一生從我眼前閃過\N{\rENG}Your life flashed before my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.41,0:09:16.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 怎麼樣?\N{\rENG}- 很值得為此死去\N{\rENG}- How was it? - Almost worth dying for.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.18,0:09:20.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們到大門了, 正準備上去\N{\rENG}We're at the front door. We're coming up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:23.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 早安，老闆, 睡得好吧?\N{\rENG}- 是的, 很好\N{\rENG}- Good morning, sir. Sleep well? - Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.32,0:09:24.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 吃早餐了嗎?\N{\rENG}- 什麼?\N{\rENG}- Eaten yet? - What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.44,0:09:26.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 吃了嗎？\N{\rENG}- 沒有\N{\rENG}- Eaten yet? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:30.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 早上好\N{\rENG}- 大衛, 你居然跑去打壁球, 我替你拖了一個鐘頭\N{\rENG}- Good morning. - David, you were playing racquetball. I've been covering you for an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:32.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,我救了你的命, 而你竟然去打球\N{\rENG}I'm saving your ass and you're playing racquetball.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.56,0:09:33.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,謝謝你, 弗裡茨\N{\rENG}Thank you, Fritz.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.77,0:09:36.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們出電梯了, 董事會很不爽\N{\rENG}We are now exiting the elevator. The board is not happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.67,0:09:39.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 早, 碧翠西\N{\rENG}- 你好, 大衛\N{\rENG}- Good morning, Beatrice. - Hello, David.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:41.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,你今天終於來了, 寇特妮想要你回復她的郵件\N{\rENG}You're in the Post today. Courtney Love called to see if you got her E-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.84,0:09:45.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,浮華世界主編想約你吃晚飯\N{\rENG}And Graydon Carter and Shelley Wanger called to see if dinner's still on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:48.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 不錯\N{\rENG}- 美術部要你決定顏色...\N{\rENG}- Cool. - Art department needs the colors-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.75,0:09:51.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 黃, 紅或白?\N{\rENG}- 早上好, 大衛\N{\rENG}- yellow and red or white? - Good morning, David.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:53.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,我有提到董事會對你遲到很生氣嗎?\N{\rENG}And did I mention the board is pissed you're late?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.59,0:09:56.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,嗨, 大衛, 等一下!\N{\rENG}Hey, David! Hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.35,0:09:57.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,哪一個?\N{\rENG}Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.56,0:09:59.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,等等, 這個嗎? 大衛!\N{\rENG}Wait. This one? David!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.09,0:10:02.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,好了, 他們都在等你\N{\rENG}Okay, they're all waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.36,0:10:05.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 你換了髮型\N{\rENG}- 是的. 大衛...\N{\rENG}- You changed your hair. - Yes. And David...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.80,0:10:08.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,做好被批鬥的準備\N{\rENG}opinions are expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.64,0:10:21.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,你夢見過董事會...那七個你稱為小矮人的嗎?\N{\rENG}Do you dream about the board- the Seven Dwarfs as you call them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:23.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,噴嚏精, 害羞鬼...\N{\rENG}Sneezy, Bashful...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.52,0:10:24.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,瞌睡蟲...\N{\rENG}Sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:25.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,開心果...\N{\rENG}Happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.85,0:10:27.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,萬事通...\N{\rENG}Doc...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.12,0:10:28.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,糊塗蛋...\N{\rENG}Dopey...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:30.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,當然, 還有暴躁鬼\N{\rENG}and of course, Grumpy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.32,0:10:31.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,艾斯本好玩嗎?\N{\rENG}How was Aspen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.99,0:10:34.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,不錯\N{\rENG}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:36.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,現在, 我要答案，馬上就要\N{\rENG}Now, I want answers and I want them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.30,0:10:46.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,進展如何?\N{\rENG}How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.51,0:10:50.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們還把我當十一歲小孩\N{\rENG}They still look at me as if I was 11 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.14,0:10:52.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,他將繼承一切\N{\rENG}He's going to inherit everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.21,0:10:54.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,全都是他的\N{\rENG}He gets it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.11,0:10:57.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,你很怕你的夢, 不是嗎?\N{\rENG}You're scared of your dreams, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:10:59.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,無論怎樣這是一場噩夢\N{\rENG}It's a nightmare either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.42,0:11:01.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,這就是對你所發生的一切的解釋?\N{\rENG}Is that how you explain what's happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:04.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 什麼?\N{\rENG}- 你的臉怎麼了?\N{\rENG}- What? - What happened to your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.42,0:11:08.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 我不再跟你談了\N{\rENG}- 你不敢給我看你的臉?\N{\rENG}- I'm not talking to you anymore. - You don't wanna show me your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.33,0:11:09.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,是的!\N{\rENG}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.47,0:11:16.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 你知道為什麼你會在這裡嗎?\N{\rENG}- 聊天, 喝咖啡...\N{\rENG}- Do you know why you're here? - Conversation, the coffee-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.50,0:11:19.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,大衛, 那些你來我往的交談...\N{\rENG}David, the part where we parry and joust...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:22.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,逐漸互相瞭解...\N{\rENG}and get to know each other bit by bit-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.64,0:11:24.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,已經, 不管用了\N{\rENG}No. No can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.44,0:11:27.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們得跳過這些, 因為你已被控謀殺\N{\rENG}We'll have to skip that because you've been charged with murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.68,0:11:31.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,四周後, 法官會決定你的命運...\N{\rENG}In four weeks, a judge will determine your fate...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.65,0:11:33.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,依據是我的診斷報告\N{\rENG}based on what I write.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.55,0:11:37.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 你最好告訴我\N{\rENG}- 根本沒有殺人\N{\rENG}- So you will talk to me. - There is no murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:41.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,根本沒殺人!\N{\rENG}There is no murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:43.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,根本沒發生過!\N{\rENG}It never happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.03,0:11:48.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 我不必跟任何人談!\N{\rENG}- 要我幫忙嗎?\N{\rENG}- I don't have to talk to anybody!\N{\rENG}- Want me to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:50.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 滾我遠點\N{\rENG}- 冷靜點,年輕人\N{\rENG}- Get the fuck away from me. - You take it easy, sunshine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.87,0:11:53.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,冷靜點, 面具, 你的整個故事都是漏洞!\N{\rENG}Take it easy, Face. Your whole story's full of holes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.57,0:11:55.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,別說了. 別說了!\N{\rENG}Stop. Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.34,0:11:58.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,請立刻離開這裡, 這裡我負責\N{\rENG}Please leave right now. I'll take responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.41,0:12:01.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,請立刻離開這裡, 他已受到控制了\N{\rENG}Please leave right now. He's got control.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:05.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,我會再找你的，靠老爸的怪胎\N{\rENG}I'm gonna get you, daddy's boy little freak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.28,0:12:08.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 我父母都死了，你這混蛋!\N{\rENG}- 夠了!\N{\rENG}- My parents are dead, you fuck!\N{\rENG}- Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.59,0:12:11.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,真的嗎?\N{\rENG}Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.82,0:12:14.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 好員警, 壞員警...\N{\rENG}- 你真的只靠你老爸嗎?\N{\rENG}- Good cop, bad cop-\N{\rENG}- That you're a daddy's boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.36,0:12:19.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,大衛.埃姆斯.西尼爾的一生\N{\rENG}Primer on David Aames Senior.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.63,0:12:21.96,CHT,,0,0,0,,我父親不是屬於二十一世紀的人\N{\rENG}My father wasn't built for the 21 st century.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.07,0:12:24.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,他從不去麥當勞, 從不\N{\rENG}He never went to McDonald's, not once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:26.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,也不看電視\N{\rENG}He never watched television, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.67,0:12:30.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,他最喜歡的雜誌仍然是電視週刊\N{\rENG}his biggest magazine is still the TVDigest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.38,0:12:33.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,他和我母親常舉行大型的文學派對\N{\rENG}He and my mother threw the grandest parties of the literary world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.01,0:12:36.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,熱氣球, 高空跳傘\N{\rENG}Ballooned. Jumped out of airplanes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.11,0:12:37.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,他追求冒險\N{\rENG}He sought adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:39.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,他的自傳是...\N{\rENG}His autobiography is the manual...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.85,0:12:42.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,紐約所有殘酷競爭的出版商的指南\N{\rENG}for every cutthroat publisher in New York City.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.22,0:12:45.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,書名叫"捍衛王國"\N{\rENG}It's called Defending the Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.12,0:12:46.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,我讀過\N{\rENG}I've read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.83,0:12:48.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,第127頁\N{\rENG}Page 127-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.93,0:12:51.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,"小大衛是個可愛的孩子"\N{\rENG}"David Jr. was a delight as a child."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.03,0:12:54.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,我有漏掉什麼嗎? 這就是他寫的所有關於你的?\N{\rENG}Did I miss something here? Was that all he wrote about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.03,0:12:59.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,我覺得他一直不能原諒這個事實...\N{\rENG}I don't think he ever got over the fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.01,0:13:02.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,我有十分...\N{\rENG}that I'm absolutely...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.64,0:13:05.08,CHT,,0,0,0,,嚴重的懼高症\N{\rENG}terrified of heights.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:08.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,接下來諷刺的是\N{\rENG}The irony continues.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.21,0:13:12.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,他和我媽被醉酒少年撞死...\N{\rENG}When he and my mother were run over by a drunken teenager...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:15.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,在十年前的新年夜裡\N{\rENG}on New Year's Eve ten years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.72,0:13:17.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,他把最重要的...\N{\rENG}he left the keys...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.36,0:13:20.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,他的王國的東西...\N{\rENG}to the kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.33,0:13:21.59,CHT,,0,0,0,,留給了我\N{\rENG}to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.69,0:13:23.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,51%的股權\N{\rENG}Fifty-one percent control.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:25.96,CHT,,0,0,0,,其餘49%股權由七名董事共有...\N{\rENG}Forty-nine percent going to a group of seven board members...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.06,0:13:30.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們每一個都認為自己是老大\N{\rENG}who all thought they were first in line.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.44,0:13:33.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,而你認為是董事會...這7個矮人...\N{\rENG}And you believe the board- the Seven Dwarfs-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:37.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,為了奪取公司控制權才陷害你入獄?\N{\rENG}put you here to take control of your company?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.68,0:13:41.34,CHT,,0,0,0,,關你屁事?\N{\rENG}What do you care?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.45,0:13:43.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們只是聊天\N{\rENG}We're just talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.98,0:13:46.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,今晚是週三晚上...\N{\rENG}And tonight's Wednesday night...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.65,0:13:50.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,通常我要和兩個女兒去Black Angus吃晚飯\N{\rENG}and I go to Black Angus for dinner with my two daughters on Wednesdays.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.56,0:13:52.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,所以我得快點走\N{\rENG}So I'll have to leave soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.92,0:13:56.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,你知道我們時間有限，對吧?\N{\rENG}You do understand that our time is limited, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.36,0:14:01.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,如果我說出來...\N{\rENG}If I talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.63,0:14:03.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,你一定覺得我瘋了\N{\rENG}you'll just think I'm crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.71,0:14:19.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒有不尊敬的意思, 想像有一個人...\N{\rENG}With all the possible respect I can offer a man...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.12,0:14:23.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,戴著塑膠面具在大談陰謀論, 大衛...\N{\rENG}wearing a latex mask and spouting conspiracy theories, David...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.36,0:14:27.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,相信我，你已經瘋了\N{\rENG}believe me, you've crossed that bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.29,0:14:29.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,祝你用餐愉快\N{\rENG}Enjoy your dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.00,0:14:35.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,人生有五個最基本的情緒, 大衛\N{\rENG}There are five basic emotions in life, David.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.40,0:14:41.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,告訴我，哪一種情緒在困擾著這個人...\N{\rENG}Tell me, what emotion gripped him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:43.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,在他進入牢房之前\N{\rENG}before he entered that cell?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.71,0:14:46.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,是罪惡感...\N{\rENG}Was it guilt...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.31,0:14:47.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,仇恨...\N{\rENG}hate...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:50.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,羞恥...\N{\rENG}shame...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.25,0:14:54.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,報復...\N{\rENG}revenge...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.36,0:15:03.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,愛?\N{\rENG}love?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.36,0:15:07.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,我完全猜錯了, 是吧?\N{\rENG}I'm completely on the wrong track, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.90,0:15:14.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,誰要冰塊?\N{\rENG}Who needs ice?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.48,0:15:19.14,CHT,,0,0,0,,大衛, 生日快樂\N{\rENG}David, happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.24,0:15:22.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,你對鞋子的品味無人能及\N{\rENG}You have got the greatest taste in shoes, bar none anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.48,0:15:26.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 艾瑪, 你見過利奈特了嗎?\N{\rENG}- 沒, 但恐怕我倆沒共同點\N{\rENG}- Emma, have you met Lynette? - I fear what we may have in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.02,0:15:31.11,CHT,,0,0,0,,大衛, 你邀請了整個奧林匹克雪板隊?\N{\rENG}David, did you invite the entire Olympic snowboarding team?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.22,0:15:32.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,今晚是我生日\N{\rENG}Tonight is my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.72,0:15:35.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 對大衛說生日快樂\N{\rENG}- 生日快樂\N{\rENG}- Say happy birthday to David. - Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.36,0:15:40.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,歡迎來到聖地\N{\rENG}Welcome to Graceland.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.40,0:15:46.30,CHT,,0,0,0,,生日快樂, 臭小子\N{\rENG}Happy birthday, you son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.40,0:15:47.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,生日快樂\N{\rENG}Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.18,0:15:51.84,CHT,,0,0,0,,嗨, 各位朋友, 大家好\N{\rENG}Hey, friends of me, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.84,0:15:56.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 玩瘋一點\N{\rENG}- 立體影像就要開始了\N{\rENG}- Let the fun ensue. - Living Stereo will be on-line soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.28,0:16:00.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,是偉大的約翰柯川(薩克斯演奏)\N{\rENG}他們會喜歡登上雜誌的\N{\rENG}It is the great John Coltrane. They would love an article on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.75,0:16:03.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,如果你喜歡,這是個很棒的原型\N{\rENG}If you like it, it's an amazing prototype.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.09,0:16:08.02,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 別,別\N{\rENG}- 不好意思\N{\rENG}- 沒事\N{\rENG}- Excuse me. - No, no. Thank you. That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.23,0:16:14.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 文學天才, 布萊恩謝比\N{\rENG}- 生日快樂\N{\rENG}- Literary god, Brian Shelby. - Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.93,0:16:17.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,還是那些相互間老套的話...\N{\rENG}And all the usual shit people say to each other-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:20.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 你好嗎?\N{\rENG}- 活在夢中, 寶貝, 活在夢中\N{\rENG}- How you doing? - Living the dream, baby, Living the dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.76,0:16:21.76,CHT,,0,0,0,,大衛.埃姆斯\N{\rENG}David Aames.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.27,0:16:24.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 我如何能享受這份厚禮?\N{\rENG}- 這禮物可是我索菲亞.塞拉諾的\N{\rENG}- To what do I owe this pleasure? - The pleasure of Sofia Serrano.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.01,0:16:27.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,我今天在圖書館認識她, 你無法想像\N{\rENG}We met today at the library, if you can believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.68,0:16:30.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,抱歉, 我的外套對你的衣櫥來說太大了\N{\rENG}Sorry about my coat. It's too big for your closet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.48,0:16:34.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 我們假裝是知識份子\N{\rENG}- 真不可思議, 我喜歡你的外套\N{\rENG}- We were pretending to be intellectuals. - It's amazing. I love your coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.35,0:16:36.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,我穿得太講究了,我意思是,太糟了\N{\rENG}I overdressed. I mean, I underdressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.72,0:16:39.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,我會假裝你們在聽我說\N{\rENG}I'll continue like you're both actually listening to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.32,0:16:41.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,你還有其他地方放嗎?\N{\rENG}Do you have another room to put it in?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.65,0:16:42.10,CHT,,0,0,0,,丹妮爾\N{\rENG}Danielle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:43.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,我都不存在了\N{\rENG}I have ceased to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:46.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,麥迪森廣場花園就在附近, 那裡也許夠大\N{\rENG}Madison Square Garden is nearby. It might fit there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.97,0:16:49.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,生日快樂\N{\rENG}Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:51.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 我們一起挑的\N{\rENG}- 謝謝你\N{\rENG}- We picked it out together. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:53.57,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們..挑的..一起\N{\rENG}We picked it out together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:16:55.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 我們\N{\rENG}- 別客氣\N{\rENG}- We. - You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.34,0:17:01.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,別含情脈脈了, 拆禮物吧\N{\rENG}Stop flirting and open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.82,0:17:05.25,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 我們去喝一杯\N{\rENG}- 是\N{\rENG}- Let's get a drink. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.35,0:17:07.61,CHT,,0,0,0,,我要拿到樓上\N{\rENG}I'll leave this upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.95,0:17:20.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,布萊恩, 過來...\N{\rENG}Brian, come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.17,0:17:23.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 我馬上回來\N{\rENG}- 好的\N{\rENG}- I'll be right back. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:27.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 聽著\N{\rENG}- 嘿, 湯米\N{\rENG}- Listen. - Hey, Tommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.11,0:17:29.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,不, 不, 別把我甩了\N{\rENG}No, no, don't blow me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.27,0:17:32.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,我都打包好了, 我準備回倫敦了, 我也知道...\N{\rENG}I'm all packed. I'm going back to London and I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.08,0:17:36.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,你讓我做另外的律師工作, 這樣就不用開除我\N{\rENG}You put me up for the other attorney's job so you didn't have to fire me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.31,0:17:39.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,這很高明, 你老爸也會這麼做\N{\rENG}That's a classy move and your father would have done the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:41.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒關係, 湯米\N{\rENG}It's okay, Tommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:44.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,我越來越不稱職了\N{\rENG}I became incompetent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.29,0:17:48.28,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒什麼比一個老古董更沒用的了\N{\rENG}Is there anything more unbecoming than an aging mascot?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.39,0:17:50.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,我關心你老爸\N{\rENG}I cared for your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.96,0:17:53.29,CHT,,0,0,0,,對他忠心耿耿\N{\rENG}I lived and breathed for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.40,0:17:55.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,那些傢伙, 那7個矮人...\N{\rENG}These guys, the Seven Dwarfs...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.97,0:17:57.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們覺得你很幼稚\N{\rENG}they think you're stupid-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.74,0:17:59.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,是公司的絆腳石, 是搗亂的人\N{\rENG}a corporate hazard, a rogue.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.94,0:18:02.53,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們正想辦法把你趕走, 大衛\N{\rENG}They are gonna find a way to get you out, David.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.64,0:18:05.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,他們會逐步奪走你的公司, 你的生活...\N{\rENG}They're lined up for your office, your life...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.01,0:18:07.41,CHT,,0,0,0,,你的地位\N{\rENG}your position.
