Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.66,0:25:43.03,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 你不是鄉下來的\N{\rENG}- 我知道\N{\rENG}- You're not from Ohio. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.13,0:25:46.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,但如果她會毀了我們的友誼, 那她可以去死了\N{\rENG}But if she fucks up our friendship, she can go to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.57,0:25:49.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不允許這種情況發生, 我們是哥們\N{\rENG}I won't allow it. We are bros.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.57,0:25:51.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 我也是這麼覺得\N{\rENG}- 你當然是\N{\rENG}- I feel the same way. - Sure you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.08,0:25:54.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 嗨\N{\rENG}- 你好嗎?\N{\rENG}- Hi.\N{\rENG}- How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.98,0:25:58.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 謝謝\N{\rENG}- 別客氣\N{\rENG}- Thank you. - You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.88,0:26:00.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,你要去哪?\N{\rENG}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.99,0:26:04.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,我是弗蘭克(電燈泡),弗蘭克必須走\N{\rENG}I am Frank, and Frank must go.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.12,0:26:08.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 什麼?\N{\rENG}- 我祝你們今晚愉快\N{\rENG}- What? - I good you bid evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.79,0:26:10.45,CHT,,0,0,0,,等等, 我和你一起走\N{\rENG}Wait. I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.43,0:26:14.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 留下來, 親愛的\N{\rENG}- 晚點我會載你回家的\N{\rENG}- Stay, baby. - I'll give you a ride home later.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.67,0:26:17.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 不, 明天我得上班\N{\rENG}- 你...\N{\rENG}- No, I have to work tomorrow. - You-
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.64,0:26:20.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,你會得到很好的照顧的\N{\rENG}You are in great hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.81,0:26:24.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,我的話只是為了安慰自己\N{\rENG}I'm just humoring myself that my opinion matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.15,0:26:33.67,CHT,,0,0,0,,你永遠體會不到那種深深的痛苦...\N{\rENG}You will never know the exquisite pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.78,0:26:36.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,一個人獨自回家...\N{\rENG}of the guy who goes home alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.02,0:26:41.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,因為沒有這痛苦, 親愛的, 那就無所謂甜蜜\N{\rENG}because without the bitter, baby, the sweet ain't as sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.99,0:26:44.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,玩的愉快\N{\rENG}Have a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.20,0:26:50.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,又是這套心酸和甜蜜\N{\rENG}The sweet and sour speech again.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.58,0:27:06.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 為什麼你有懼高症?\N{\rENG}- 很多人都有\N{\rENG}- Why are you scared of heights? - Many people are scared of heights.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.15,0:27:08.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不是怕高, 而是感到困擾\N{\rENG}It's not the height that bothers me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.42,0:27:11.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,是那種壓力在威脅著我\N{\rENG}It's the impact that terrifies me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.10,0:27:19.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不會待太久\N{\rENG}I won't stay long.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.80,0:27:21.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,嘿, 保羅\N{\rENG}Hey, Paolo.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.07,0:27:24.66,CHT,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\rENG}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.77,0:27:26.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,我得帶你去散步\N{\rENG}I have to take you for a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.04,0:27:30.94,CHT,,0,0,0,,幸好有它保護著你, 它是個猛犬\N{\rENG}I'm glad he protects you. He's a lethal canine.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.04,0:27:34.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,我喜歡住這裡, 我也懶得打掃\N{\rENG}I love living here, and I refuse to clean up.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.81,0:27:36.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒事\N{\rENG}No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.31,0:27:39.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,我得拼命打工才住的起這裡\N{\rENG}I have to work around the clock to keep this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.78,0:27:43.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 你真的是個舞蹈家\N{\rENG}- 十四年了\N{\rENG}- You really are a dancer. - For 14 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.49,0:27:46.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,但我可不會跳得像你那樣\N{\rENG}But I don't dance like you dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.16,0:27:49.56,CHT,,0,0,0,,想喝什麼嗎?\N{\rENG}Do you want something to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.66,0:27:51.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rENG}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.80,0:27:57.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,嘿, 真乖, 乖孩子\N{\rENG}Hey, beautiful, beautiful boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.00,0:28:00.73,CHT,,0,0,0,,晚餐想吃什麼?\N{\rENG}What do you want for dinner tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.84,0:28:02.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,想吃炸雞嗎?\N{\rENG}Do you want fried chicken?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.22,0:28:13.81,CHT,,0,0,0,,我喜歡你的生活\N{\rENG}I like your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.92,0:28:16.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,好吧, 這是我的, 你不能擁有它\N{\rENG}Well, it's mine and you can't have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.42,0:28:22.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,我不想知道這照片背後的故事\N{\rENG}I don't wanna know the story behind this photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.66,0:28:26.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 誰是塞爾吉奧?\N{\rENG}- 這是個綽號\N{\rENG}- Who's Sergio?\N{\rENG}- It's a nickname.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.56,0:28:29.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 你外號叫塞爾吉奧?\N{\rENG}- 說來話長\N{\rENG}- Your nickname is Sergio?\N{\rENG}- It's a long story.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.60,0:28:32.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們互相都還不熟\N{\rENG}And we don't know each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.90,0:28:35.80,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 這麼多秘密啊\N{\rENG}- 因為我是個軍火商(在調侃大衛的姓氏)\N{\rENG}- So many secrets. - That's because I'm an arms dealer.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.91,0:28:38.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 我從沒認識過軍火商\N{\rENG}- 現在認識了\N{\rENG}- I've never known an arms dealer. - You do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.24,0:28:42.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,那你呢?\N{\rENG}你的綽號是什麼?\N{\rENG}What about you? What's your nickname?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.95,0:28:49.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,國民老二\N{\rENG}Citizen Dildo.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.09,0:28:54.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,你不能在這呆一晚上\N{\rENG}You are not staying over.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.33,0:29:02.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,別做老闆, 做個藝術家, 或者軍火商\N{\rENG}Never run a company. Stay an artist. Stay an arms dealer.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.37,0:29:05.89,CHT,,0,0,0,,拜託, 不知為何我無法同情你\N{\rENG}Oh, please. Somehow I can't play the violin for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.00,0:29:10.00,CHT,,0,0,0,,雖然, 能影響那麼多人的生活一定很困難\N{\rENG}Although, it must be difficult controlling all those people's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.04,0:29:16.88,CHT,,0,0,0,,派對上每個和你有聯繫的人某種程度上都靠你吃飯\N{\rENG}Everyone at that party is connected to you for survival in some way.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.98,0:29:18.04,CHT,,0,0,0,,看起來\N{\rENG}It seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.92,0:29:23.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,結過婚嗎?\N{\rENG}Ever been married?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.46,0:29:30.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒有,你曾經接受過一萬兩千個男人的求婚?\N{\rENG}Did you ever accept any of your 12,000 proposals?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.33,0:29:32.82,CHT,,0,0,0,,一萬兩千零八個. 沒有\N{\rENG}Twelve thousand and eight. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.93,0:29:36.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,然後你搬到紐約來跳舞,畫畫, 表演和賣軍火?\N{\rENG}And you moved to New York to dance, paint, act and deal arms?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.80,0:29:38.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rENG}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.70,0:29:41.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,你想聽傑夫.巴克利還是維姬.卡爾?\N{\rENG}Do you wanna hear Jeff Buckley or Vicki Carr?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.97,0:29:43.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,傑夫.巴克利還是維姬.卡爾?\N{\rENG}Jeff Buckley or Vicki Carr?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.14,0:29:47.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,一起聽\N{\rENG}Both simultaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.21,0:29:52.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,每個人都說,"別到紐約"\N{\rENG}Everyone said, "Don't go to New York."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.15,0:29:54.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,我只是覺得好事總會發生...\N{\rENG}I just think good things will happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.35,0:29:57.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,如果你是好人有好的心態的話\N{\rENG}if you're a good person with a good attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.12,0:29:58.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,你不覺得嗎?\N{\rENG}Don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.03,0:30:03.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,你覺得我很天真嗎?\N{\rENG}You think I'm naive?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.09,0:30:07.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,不, 絕對沒有\N{\rENG}No. I really don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.23,0:30:09.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,我真的喜歡上她了\N{\rENG}I dug her completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.30,0:30:14.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,忽然間...我發現了紐約最後一個單純的女孩\N{\rENG}Somehow I'd found the last semi-guyless girl in New York City.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.84,0:30:18.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,我得睡覺了\N{\rENG}I have to get to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.51,0:30:22.64,CHT,,0,0,0,,說實話, 白天我還有個工作是牙醫助理\N{\rENG}Truthfully, I also work mornings as a dental assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.42,0:30:26.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,天哪, 我都找錯牙醫了\N{\rENG}Boy, am I going to the wrong dentist.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.95,0:30:31.05,CHT,,0,0,0,,而你都沒有馬上就想和她上床?\N{\rENG}And you didn't immediately wanna sleep with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.16,0:30:34.78,CHT,,0,0,0,,額, 你知道, 我是個延遲享樂者\N{\rENG}Well, you know, I'm a pleasure delayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.09,0:30:39.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 那是什麼意思?\N{\rENG}- 延遲享樂者?\N{\rENG}- How does that work?\N{\rENG}- Pleasure delayer?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.90,0:30:42.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,你不知道?\N{\rENG}You don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.57,0:30:45.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,你保持和一個人順其自然的交往...\N{\rENG}You keep a relationship casual...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.27,0:30:48.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,直到一個絕佳的機會\N{\rENG}until the absolute breaking point.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.91,0:30:53.54,CHT,,0,0,0,,然後在一個晚上..或中午...或早上...\N{\rENG}And then one evening or afternoon or morning-
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.64,0:30:56.20,CHT,,0,0,0,,那得花上好幾個月\N{\rENG}it could be months from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.31,0:30:59.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,你知道這是怎麼一回事\N{\rENG}You know how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.98,0:31:03.21,CHT,,0,0,0,,不, 說實話不知道\N{\rENG}No, actually I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.32,0:31:06.35,CHT,,0,0,0,,我結婚22年了\N{\rENG}I've been married for 22 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.46,0:31:08.65,CHT,,0,0,0,,你還要和女兒吃飯\N{\rENG}You've got dinner with your daughters.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.63,0:31:12.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒錯, 我知道\N{\rENG}That's right, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.23,0:31:15.36,CHT,,0,0,0,,那時我有各種招數對付女人...\N{\rENG}Back then I had intricate systems with women...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.47,0:31:17.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,你不會相信\N{\rENG}you wouldn't believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.64,0:31:21.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,比如?\N{\rENG}Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.64,0:31:28.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,嘿, 醫生, 別再為不是單身而難過了...\N{\rENG}Hey, Doc, don't get melancholy over the 30 seconds you were single...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.71,0:31:30.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,很久以前的了\N{\rENG}a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.98,0:31:33.85,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 你覺得我是這樣嗎?\N{\rENG}- 是的\N{\rENG}- That's what you think I'm doing? - Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.85,0:31:36.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,你也許是對的\N{\rENG}You might be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.72,0:31:41.09,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們繼續吧, 時間不等人\N{\rENG}Let's continue. Time is not our friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.76,0:32:16.32,CHT,,0,0,0,,只限於缺點, 我們只能畫這些\N{\rENG}Just our shortcomings, that's all we're allowed to draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.06,0:32:21.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,我從來沒畫得這麼像過\N{\rENG}I've never drawn such a true likeness before.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.97,0:32:26.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,我畫好了\N{\rENG}Mine's finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.37,0:32:27.77,CHT,,0,0,0,,這麼快?\N{\rENG}Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.58,0:32:35.48,CHT,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\rENG}Done.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.38,0:32:42.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 你是這麼看我的嗎?\N{\rENG}- 也許錢畫得還不夠多\N{\rENG}- That's how you see me? - Maybe I didn't add enough money.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.49,0:32:46.18,CHT,,0,0,0,,不, 你簡直畫得入木三分\N{\rENG}No, something you'd see on a wall in a steak house in hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.29,0:32:48.38,CHT,,0,0,0,,太棒了, 簽名吧\N{\rENG}It's wonderful. Sign it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.90,0:32:56.63,CHT,,0,0,0,,讓我看你的\N{\rENG}Let's see yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.22,0:32:58.49,CHT,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rENG}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.10,0:33:00.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,把它給我\N{\rENG}Give me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.45,0:33:15.42,CHT,,0,0,0,,我很內疚\N{\rENG}I feel bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.52,0:33:17.68,CHT,,0,0,0,,你說要畫滑稽的\N{\rENG}You said to draw a caricature.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.79,0:33:20.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,我知道, 但沒辦法\N{\rENG}I know. I couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.72,0:33:22.92,CHT,,0,0,0,,我看見你就是這樣的\N{\rENG}I saw you like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.16,0:33:28.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,畫得很好\N{\rENG}It's very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.23,0:33:32.46,CHT,,0,0,0,,我要賣給你\N{\rENG}I'll sell it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.57,0:33:35.33,CHT,,0,0,0,,你這壞人\N{\rENG}You monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.44,0:33:36.60,CHT,,0,0,0,,這多少錢?\N{\rENG}How much for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.61,0:33:41.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,一個吻\N{\rENG}One kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.08,0:33:49.58,CHT,,0,0,0,,這笑容太令我陶醉了\N{\rENG}That smile is gonna be the end of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.06,0:33:54.62,CHT,,0,0,0,,明天你朋友打給你怎麼辦?\N{\rENG}And what happens when your friend calls you tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.56,0:34:01.16,CHT,,0,0,0,,他只比我早遇見你幾個鐘頭, 他也會這麼做的\N{\rENG}He just met you a few hours before me. He'd do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.27,0:34:03.93,CHT,,0,0,0,,我覺得友情對你很重要\N{\rENG}I see that friendship is important to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.03,0:34:05.90,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒錯, 是的\N{\rENG}It is. It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.00,0:34:09.87,CHT,,0,0,0,,我是他最好的朋友...\N{\rENG}And as his best friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.97,0:34:14.27,CHT,,0,0,0,,我知道他正準備完成一部關於缺憾和拒絕的小說\N{\rENG}I know he's trying to finish a novel about inadequacy and rejection.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.38,0:34:17.44,CHT,,0,0,0,,所以我在這呆的越久,對他的前途就越好\N{\rENG}So the longer that I stay, the better it is for his career.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.58,0:34:22.55,CHT,,0,0,0,,你的前途才是我擔心的\N{\rENG}Your career is the one I'd worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.66,0:34:30.79,CHT,,0,0,0,,對不起\N{\rENG}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.73,0:34:34.70,CHT,,0,0,0,,不, 不, 其實你說得沒錯\N{\rENG}No. No, you're more right than you even know.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.30,0:34:39.24,CHT,,0,0,0,,我曾經是那種傢伙...\N{\rENG}I used to be one of those guys that just...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.54,0:34:43.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,雪板就是他的生活...\N{\rENG}snowboarded through his life...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.17,0:34:45.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,沒有目標...\N{\rENG}with no focus...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.44,0:34:47.97,CHT,,0,0,0,,完全沒有\N{\rENG}whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.08,0:34:49.98,CHT,,0,0,0,,你幾時改變的?\N{\rENG}When did you change?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.08,0:34:52.07,CHT,,0,0,0,,大概五分鐘前\N{\rENG}About five minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.82,0:34:57.01,CHT,,0,0,0,,每一分鐘都有可能會改變你的生活\N{\rENG}Every passing minute is another chance to turn it all around.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.73,0:35:07.72,CHT,,0,0,0,,對於那些認為你是個騙子的人?\N{\rENG}And to those who think that you're a charlatan?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.83,0:35:09.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\rENG}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.37,0:35:11.83,CHT,,0,0,0,,這種觀點是把人冷凍起來...\N{\rENG}The perception of a head frozen somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.94,0:35:14.50,CHT,,0,0,0,,等待復蘇, 聽起來像科幻小說\N{\rENG}waiting for reanimation sounds like science fiction.
