Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.64,0:35:22.74,CHT,,0,0,0,,這是新科技的最前沿\N{\rENG}It is at the frontier of a new science.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.85,0:35:24.37,CHT,,0,0,0,,生命延續\N{\rENG}Life Extension.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.68,0:35:27.95,CHT,,0,0,0,,你如何實現這樣的構想呢?\N{\rENG}How do you accomplish such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.05,0:35:30.75,CHT,,0,0,0,,我看過這個30遍了\N{\rENG}I've seen this 30 times.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.85,0:35:32.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,生命充滿了意外\N{\rENG}Life is full of surprises.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.79,0:35:37.52,CHT,,0,0,0,,但最大的意外就是生命不是非得終結\N{\rENG}But the greatest surprise of all is that this doesn't have to end ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.63,0:35:40.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,我們報導過他, 他擁有半個亞利桑那州\N{\rENG}We did a story on this guy. He owns half of Arizona.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.53,0:35:43.69,CHT,,0,0,0,,- 他是騙子嗎?\N{\rENG}- 誰知道呢?\N{\rENG}- Is he a fraud?\N{\rENG}- How would you ever know?
