Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.14,0:35:48.26,CHT,,0,0,0,,你能把人解凍嗎?\N{\rENG}Can you unfreeze a human life?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.37,0:35:51.17,CHT,,0,0,0,,以小狗班尼為例, 班尼是只小狗\N{\rENG}Take the case of Benny the dog. Benny's a dog.
